    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-size: 9pt; font-style: italic;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Мерос қолдирувчини дафн этиш билан боғлиқ </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>харажатларни қоплаш тўғрисида </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span>Ф А Р М О Й И Ш</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#2}Нотариал округ номи</span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#3}Фармойиш тасдиқланган сана </span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мен – Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#4}Нотариус жойлашган манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">даги </span><span class=\"structures structure-31\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#31}Давлат нотариал идораси нотариуси</span><span class=\"structures structure-32\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; display: none;\">{#32}Хусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи нотариус</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да </span><span class=\"structures structure-31 structure-7\" style=\"className:31 7; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">{#31}(<span class=\"leading\"></span>-сонли нотариал идораси рақами</span><span class=\"structures structure-31\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">{#31})</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> нотариал идорага </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#8}Мерос қолдирувчининг вафот этган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да вафот этган </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#9}Мархумнинг яшаган манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#12}Мархумнинг охирги рўйхатда турган жойи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-уйда пропискада турувчи – </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#13}Мархумнинг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">ни дафн этиш ва унинг қабрини обод қилиш билан боғлиқ харажатларни қоплаш юзасидан фуқаро </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#14}Ариза билан мурожаат қилган шахснинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> томонидан берилган аризани кўриб чиқиб, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 1144-моддаси ва «Нотариат тўғрисида»ги Ўзбекистон Республикаси Қонунининг 57-моддасига асосан</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;\">фармойиш қиламан:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Аризачи рўйхатдан ўтилган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-уйда пропискада турувчи – </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#20}Аризачининг туғилган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-йилда туғилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}Аризачининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">га (паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-27\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#27}Аризачининг паспорт серияси ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#22}Аризачига паспорт берган ҳудуд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ИИБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#23}Аризачига паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда берилган) марҳум </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#13}Мархумнинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">ни дафн этиш ва унинг қабрини обод қилиш билан боғлиқ харажатларни қоплаш мақсадида, марҳумнинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#24}Марҳумнинг бойликлари мавжуд банк номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> банки </span><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#25}Банк филиали</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> филиалининг </span><span class=\"structures structure-28\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#28}Мархумнинг ҳисоб рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ҳисоб рақамида сақланаётган суммадан </span><span class=\"structures structure-26\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#26}Банк ҳисоб рақамида сақланаётган сумма миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> сўм берилсин.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ушбу фармойиш икки нусхада тузилди, улардан бир нусхаси </span><span class=\"structures structure-31\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#31}Давлат нотариал идораси нотариуси</span><span class=\"structures structure-32\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; display: none;\">{#32}Хусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи нотариус</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">(</span><span class=\"structures structure-31 structure-7\" style=\"className:31 7; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">{#31}Нотариус идораси рақами</span><span class=\"structures structure-31\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">{#31}-сон нотариал идорасида</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\"> очилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-29\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">{#29}Мерос иши рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">-сон мерос ишида сақланади)</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span>иккинчи нусхаси фуқаро </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}Аризачининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">га берилди.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариус: <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: italic;\">Эслатма:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: italic;\"> Ушбу фармойиш нотариал ҳаракат деб ҳисобланмайди, шунинг учун давлат божи ундирилмайди.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
